Usage: roulbot [INSTR]

Trading bot that tries a roulette strategy.

  -H, --host=NAME       Connect to NAME.
  -d, --daemonise       Detach from terminal.
  -Q, --qty=Q[+H]       Post a quantity of Q (and H hidden),
                        default: 1+0
  -T, --target=X        X can be +P (for additive target) or P% for
                        relative target.  The sign determines whether
                        to go long or short.
